metadata.name: Stereo Flower 1/1
metadata.description:
The map is a pattern. The blueprint to a functional garment, a complex configuration applies mathematical knowhow. Packing problems posed by aesthetic properties. Asymmetric denim bodycon dress, fitted tank straps, contrast topstitching, bright bumblebee yellow tee, puffed epoch print jacket, ribbed material cuffs. 

Synth Graph: a center front view portrait, 2012, photograph of a beautiful tanned female model wearing a detailed red floral printed yellow and blue puffy jacket, with a ripped denim miniskirt, black high top sneakers, bright yellow socks, blue hair, red lipstick, walking down manhattan in the 2000s, highly detailed. Sampler: plms, steps: 75, scale: 11.
